caption;Versi 2
p;Wherever to go my heart is ready
p;Lord, I know Thy guidance never, never fails
p;Help me to obey and to bear Thy cross,
p;Lord I know Thy guidance never fails.
p;Whether in a city or in a virgin land
p;Souls Thou created are same precious in Thy sight.
p;Wherever to go my heart is ready
p;O Lord, help me to love whom You love.
